:'''Regin:''' But those pencil-pushing bureaucrats are always trying to make trouble for me!
:'''Regin:''' I just need your help with this very simple thing: Give this thesis to the Supreme Guardian. Let her see what I've achieved.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why don't you go yourself?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301120123-->
