:{{DIcon}} Have you made any progress with your research?
::'''Regin:''' Of course, I have. I am soon going to find a suitable place to construct the time tunnel &mdash;
::'''Regin:''' &mdash; Also, keep your voice down. Don't disrupt me from constructing the time tunnel model!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Model? Where's this model?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024185-->
:::'''Regin:''' It's right here, obviously. Can you not see my big brain? A genius does not require the help of external tools, including pen and paper. All a genius needs is their own brain!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Where do you plan on making the tunnel?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024187-->
:::'''Regin:''' Easy. The central point of the time tunnel is within the mine tunnels in the Underworld!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501024189-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024189-->
::'''Regin:''' Don't doubt me! Think about it. Contact with the Underworld has been cut off for so many years, and now the Underworld is suddenly open. I believe that the reason behind all this must be the Big Universe time tunnel. From this deduction, we know that...
::'''Regin:''' We know that... The central point of this time tunnel is in the mine! It's a logical conclusion backed by evidence. Wouldn't you say?
::'''Regin:''' In short, I firmly believe that this is the correct direction for my work. All I have to do is get down into the Underworld mines and inspect the site. That will absolutely lead me to solid evidence that supports my magnificent theory!
::'''Regin:''' ...If I can get the funding I need.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
