:{{DIcon}} How's your science journal doing?
::'''Regin:''' In two words: On fire. Just a few months after launch, I've already received hundreds of scientific papers from across society.
::'''Regin:''' While most are mediocre, a few articles caught my eye, like ''The Possibility of Creating a Perpetual Motion Machine Using Black Holes'' and ''Evidence Supporting the Existence of Water Monkey Species''...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's true what they say, there are undiscovered geniuses among us.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049105-->
:::'''Regin:''' That's precisely why I named it ''Citizen Science''. For too long, the power to define science has been monopolized by complacent academics, holding back Belobog's scientific advancement.
:::'''Regin:''' But the renaissance of science is upon us. Under my leadership, Belobog is on the verge of a technological revolution.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sounds like a compendium of pseudoscience, doesn't it?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049108-->
:::'''Regin:''' I understand where you're coming from because you're a normal person without insight into advanced theories.
:::'''Regin:''' Let me put it this way, many truths now universally acknowledged across the universe were considered pseudoscience just a few Amber Eras ago.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wallace's investment has gone down the drain.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049111-->
:::'''Regin:''' Unlike you, Wallace isn't shortsighted. Even though he may not grasp all the detailed theories, he respects the spirit of scientific inquiry, and... well, he also has deep pockets.
:::'''Regin:''' Anyway, scientific research is a long-term investment, and I believe he has the patience for it.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504049113-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049113-->
::'''Regin:''' Given your extensive travels, if you ever come across anything intriguing, feel free to contribute to ''Citizen Science''.
::'''Regin:''' And don't worry about the fee, we won't shortchange you.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
