:::'''Regin:''' This isn't surprising. Most Belobogians look similar in one way or another! You must've been mistaken, I don't have a twin brother.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Could it be you from a parallel universe?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_801880105-->
